Author
@{b}Dark Conquest Was Written With AMOSPro v2.00@{ub}
@endnode

@node Loading
@{fg highlight}Running the Game@{fg text}

@{fg highlight}@{b}!!!BACKUP THE ORIGINAL DISK NOW!!!@{ub}@{fg text}

Dark Conquest is run from Workbench. Load Workbench and insert the
Dark Conquest disk into a disk drive. When its icon appears, double-click to
open the disk's window. To run the program, double click on the DarkConquest
icon.

If you have installed Dark Conquest and wish to run it from there, open
your hard disk window and find the drawer containing Dark Conquest (the
path you chose when you installed the program). Double-click the DarkConquest
icon to run the program.
@endnode

